high_descs: Go forward then turn left to face the chair with the box on it.
Pick up the watch on the chair.
Turn to face the box on the chair
Put the watch in the box.
Pick up the box with the watch in it.
Turn right, then go straight, then turn right to face the coffee table.
Place the box in the center of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a watch in a box on the table.

high_descs: Go straight, turn right at the coffee table, go straight to the chair with the box on it.
Take the watch to the right of the box from the chair.
Go in front of the box on the chair.
Put the watch in the box.
Take the box from the chair.
turn right, go straight, turn right to the coffee table, go to the coffee table.
Put the box on the coffee table to the right of the left most book.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a watch in it on a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left at coffee table and go to red chair with open box on it.
Pick up watch next to the box on the chair.
Position self in front of box on chair.
Place watch in open box on red chair.
Pick up open box with watch in it.
Turn around and go to coffee table.
Place open box with watch on coffee table, closer to the book on the left and the laptop.  The keys and other book should be to the right of the box.
anns.task_desc: Putting a watch in a box and moving a box to a table.

high_descs: Walk towards the table turn left and face the pink couch
Pick up the watch on the couch
Turn to your left, turn right face the box on the couch
Put the watch inside the box
Pick up the box on the couch
Turn to your right head to the center table
Put the box on the center table
anns.task_desc: Put the watch on the box place it on the table

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the watch on the pink chair.
Pick up the watch from the pink chair.
Walk to the box on the pink chair.
Place the watch into the box on the pink chair.
Pick up the box from the pink chair.
Turn around and walk to the table in the middle of the room.
Place the box to the left of the keys on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a watch in it on the wooden table.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the red chair with the cardboard box on it.
Pick up the wristwatch from the chair.
Move slightly left to face the box.
Put the watch into the cardboard box.
Pick up the boxed watch.
Turn around and go to face the center of the coffee table.
Place the box on the center of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a wristwatch in it in the center of a coffee table.
